# Map AI-assisted agent identities to a generic contributor so
# they don't appear in `git shortlog` or GitHub's Insights →
# Contributors graph. The original commits still exist; this
# only affects how attribution is displayed.
#
# Format: canonical-name <canonical-email> <commit-name> <commit-email>
